<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Application Submitted | T&S Traffic Control</title>
  <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
  <script>tailwindcss.config={theme:{extend:{colors:{brand:{50:'#EBF3FF',100:'#D6E7FF',200:'#ADC9FF',300:'#85ABFF',400:'#5C8DFF',500:'#2B7FFF',600:'#1D6AE5',700:'#1554CC',800:'#0D3FB2',900:'#052A99',950:'#001A66'}}}}}</script>
</head>
<body class="min-h-screen bg-gradient-to-br from-brand-600 via-brand-700 to-brand-900 flex items-center justify-center p-4">
  <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-2xl p-8 md:p-12 max-w-lg w-full text-center">
    <!-- Success icon -->
    <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-green-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6">
      <svg class="w-10 h-10 text-green-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/>
      </svg>
    </div>

    <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Application Submitted!</h1>
    <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">
      Thank you for completing the T&S Traffic Control soft induction. Your application has been received and is being reviewed by our team.
    </p>

    <div class="bg-brand-50 border border-brand-200 rounded-xl p-4 mb-6 text-left">
      <h3 class="font-semibold text-brand-800 mb-2">What happens next?</h3>
      <ul class="text-sm text-brand-700 space-y-2">
        <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-brand-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg>
          Our team will review your application and documents
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-brand-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg>
          If approved, you'll be invited for a hard induction (in-person training)
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-brand-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg>
          We'll contact you via the phone number or email you provided
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-3 mb-6">
      <img src="/images/logo-colour.jpg" alt="T&S" class="h-10 w-auto rounded-lg">
      <div class="text-left">
        <p class="font-bold text-gray-900 text-sm">T&S Traffic Control</p>
        <p class="text-xs text-gray-500">"A Safe Way Home"</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <p class="text-xs text-gray-400">You can close this page now.</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
